\c 3
\s Shamwari nhatu dzaDhaniyeri dzinoramba kunamata chifananidzo chaNebhukadhinezari
\p
\v 1 Nebhukadhinezari mambo wakaita chifananidzo chegoridhe; kureba kwacho kwaiva makubhiti makumi matanhatu, kufara kwacho makubhiti matanhatu; akachimisa pabani reDhura mudunhu reBhabhironi.
\v 2 Uye Nebhukadhinezari mambo wakatuma kunounganidza machinda, vabati, nevatungamiriri, madzishe, vabati vehomwe, varayiri, vatongi, nevese vatungamiriri vematunhu, kuti vauye pakugadzwa kwechifananidzo Nebhukadhinezari mambo chaaiva amisa.
\v 3 Ipapo machinda, vabati, nevatungamiriri, madzishe, vabati vehomwe, varayiri, vatongi, nevese vatungamiriri vematunhu, vakaungana pakugadzwa kwechifananidzo Nebhukadhinezari mambo chaaiva amisa; ndokumira pamberi pechifananidzo Nebhukadhinezari chaaiva amisa.
\v 4 Zvino mudanidziri wakadanidzira nesimba \add achiti\add*: Munorayirwa, imwi vanhu, marudzi, nendimi,
\v 5 panguva yamunonzwa kurira kwehwamanda, rutsanga, mbira, rudimbwa, mutengeranwa, marimba, nemarudzi ese ezviridzwa, muwire pasi mushumire chifananidzo chegoridhe Nebhukadhinezari mambo chaakamisa.
\v 6 Zvino ani nani asingawiri pasi nekushumira, panguva iyoyo achakandirwa mukati mevira remoto rinopfuta.
\v 7 Naizvozvo panguva iyoyo vanhu vese pavakanzwa kurira kwehwamanda, rutsanga, mbira, rudimbwa, mutengeranwa, nemarudzi ese ezviridzwa, vanhu vese, marudzi, nendimi, vakawira pasi kushumira chifananidzo chegoridhe, Nebhukadhinezari mambo chaaiva amisa.
\p
\v 8 Naizvozvo panguva iyoyo vamwe VaKaradhiya vakaswedera vakapomera VaJudha.
\v 9 Vakapindura vakati kuna mambo Nebhukadhinezari: Imwi mambo, raramai nekusingaperi.
\v 10 Imwi mambo makaita chirevo, kuti munhu umwe neumwe achanzwa kurira kwehwamanda, rutsanga, mbira, rudimbwa, mutengeranwa, nemarimba, nemarudzi ese ezviridzwa, awire pasi ndokushumira chifananidzo chegoridhe.
\v 11 Uye ani nani asingawiri pasi nekushumira, anofanira kukandwa mukati mevira remoto rinopfuta.
\v 12 Pane vamwe VaJudha vamakagadza pamusoro pebasa rese redunhu reBhabhironi, Shadhireki, Meshaki, naAbhedhinego; varume ava, ishe, havana kuva nehanya nemwi, havashumiri vamwari venyu, uye havanamati chifananidzo chegoridhe chamakamisa.
\p
\v 13 Ipapo Nebhukadhinezari mukutsamwa nekupfuta wakaraira kuuiswa kwaShadhireki, Meshaki, naAbhedhinego. Zvino vakaunza varume ava pamberi pamambo.
\v 14 Nebhukadhinezari wakapindura ndokuti kwavari: Maune here, Shadhireki, Meshaki, naAbhedhinego, \add kuti\add* hamushumiri vamwari vangu, uye hamunamati chifananidzo chegoridhe chandakamisa?
\v 15 Ikozvino kana makagadzirira kuti panguva yamuchanzwa kurira kwehwamanda, rutsanga, mbira, rudimbwa, mutengeranwa, nemarimba, nemarudzi ese ezviridzwa, muchawira pasi mushumire chifananidzo chandakaita, \add zvakanaka\add*; asi kana musingashumiri muchakandirwa panguva iyoyo mukati mevira remoto rinopfuta. Zvino ndiyani Mwari uyo achakununurai kubva mumaoko angu?
\v 16 Shadhireki, Meshaki naAbhedhinego vakapindura ndokuti kuna mambo: Imwi Nebhukadhinezari, hatitsvaki kukupindurai panyaya iyi.
\v 17 Kana zvikaitika, Mwari wedu watinoshumira angagona kutinunura pavira remoto rinopfuta; uye iye acha\add ti\add*nunura paruoko rwenyu, mambo.
\v 18 Asi kana zvikasadaro, ngazvizikanwe kwamuri, imwi mambo, kuti hatingashumiri vamwari venyu uye hatinganamati chifananidzo chegoridhe chamakamisa.
\p
\v 19 Ipapo Nebhukadhinezari wakazara nekupfuta, uye chimiro chechiso chake chikashandukira Shadhireki, Meshaki, naAbhedhinego; akapindura ndokuraira kuti vavesere vira kakapetwa kanomwe kupfuura zvaraifanira kuveserwa.
\v 20 Zvino wakaraira varume vaiva nesimba kwazvo vaiva muhondo yake kusunga Shadhireki, Meshaki, naAbhedhinego, kukandira muvira remoto rinopfuta.
\v 21 Ipapo varume avo vakasungwa vakapfeka nguvo refu dzavo, mabhurukwa avo, nenguwani dzavo, ne\add dzimwe\add* nguvo dzavo, ndokuwisirwa mukati mevira remoto rinopfuta.
\v 22 Naizvozvo nekuda kwekuti shoko ramambo raiva rakapinza, nevira richipisa kwazvo, mupfuto wemoto wakauraya varume avo vakatora Shadhireki, Meshaki, naAbhedhinego.
\v 23 Zvino varume ava vatatu Shadhireki, Meshaki, naAbhedhinego, vakawira pasi vakasungwa mukati mevira remoto rinopfuta.
\v 24 Ipapo mambo Nebhukadhinezari akavhunduswa, ndokukurumidza kusimuka, akapindura ndokuti kumakurukota ake: Hatina kuwisira varume vatatu vakasungwa mukati memoto here? Vakapindura ndokuti kuna mambo: Ichokwadi, mambo.
\v 25 Akapindura ndokuti: Tarirai, ini ndinoona varume vana vakasununguka, vanofamba mukati memoto, uye kusina kukuvara pavari, uye chimiro chewechina chakaita semwanakomana wevamwari.
\p
\v 26 Ipapo Nebhukadhinezari wakaswedera kumukova wevira remoto raipfuta, akataura ndokuti: Shadhireki, Meshaki, naAbhedhinego, imwi varanda vaMwari Wekumusoro-soro, budai muuye. Ipapo Shadhireki, Meshaki, naAbhedhinego vakabuda mukati memoto.
\v 27 Zvino machinda, varayiri, nemadzishe, nemakurukota amambo vakaungana vakaona varume ava, kuti moto wakange washaiwa simba pamiviri yavo, nevhudzi remisoro yavo rakange risina kutsva, nenguvo dzavo refu dzakange dzisina kubvuraudzwa; kunyange munhuhwi wemoto wakange usina kusvika kwavari.
\v 28 Nebhukadhinezari akapindura ndokuti: Mwari waShadhireki, Meshaki, naAbhedhinego ngaarumbidzwe, iye akatuma mutumwa wake, akanunura varanda vake vakange vachivimba naye, ivo vakange varamba shoko ramambo, vakaisa miviri yavo, kuti varege kushumira uye varege kunamata mwari upi neupi kunze kwaMwari wavo.
\v 29 Naizvozvo ndinotema chirevo, kuti vanhu vese, marudzi, nendimi, vanotaura zvisina kufanira pamusoro paMwari waShadhireki, Meshaki, naAbhedhinego, vatemwe-temwe, neimba yavo iitwe durunhuru; nokuti hakuna umwe mwari anogona kurwira saizvozvo.
\v 30 Ipapo mambo akawedzera ukuru hwaShadhireki, Meshaki, naAbhedhinego padunhu reBhabhironi.
